  "texts": [
    "However, SDN is prepared by several planes, such as the data plane, control plane, and application plane 54 as shown in Fig. 4.",
    "Moreover, it is a networking paradigm that is capable of offering centralized controllers for any operational data efficiently.",
    "These SDN controllers provide scalability, flexibility, and privacy, configure the network and network services, and enhance the network's performance appropriately.",
    "For this model, SDN's role is to allow efficient support for the streaming of data together with a saved area of this huge data 52.",
    "Furthermore, it includes IoT forwarding devices such as routers, switches, firewalls, BSN, SDP, and Healthcare Provider's Wallet (HPW)."
  ]
}